:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"村上本國境之南咁<br />\n<br />\n好貪心"},{"pid":"92526f130d954d637bc802ecb8794942e875a410","tid":948642,"uid":109462,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"d14139b29d5a63f29059a29c7859dd2284206eb2","tid":948642,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"起歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"佢哋個年代同各有家室嘅情況應該起《再見亦是朋友》先啱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2FpxjGoQmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk2FpxjGoQmo&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d161d9e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2FpxjGoQmo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">期望你轉身　與我相廝守　輾轉錯　錯了未願放手<br />\n緣盡我早知　卻也等候　只因你冷暖自願透</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">對你的愛心　亦已看透　但我知此刻美夢不會久　<br />\n緣分太感傷　盼你多見諒　不相見　免卻日後惆悵</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長夜冷冰冰　每次溫暖後　癡癡愛　我拒絕任你走　<br />\n明白你處境　我也得接受　不可說　再見亦是朋友</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">看你心痛苦　沒法去補救　若再不歸家　找不到借口　<br />\n凝望你眼睛　有更深感受　癡癡意　放棄亦未能夠</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">寧願我委屈　決意不退後　真的愛　我倆靜候已久　<br />\n期望再期望　這裡一個夢　不消散　永遠墜入迷惘</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你我皆痛苦　沒法愛得夠　蜜意低低斟　飲千樽美酒</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">惟願我留下　愛你千千個晚上</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">惟願你　　　留下</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">輕撫你百遍亦未曾夠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">輕撫我百遍亦未曾夠</span>"},{"pid":"5f5461eaf2d21f852220b11f99981440bd3f6b1c","tid":948642,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:49:41.000Z","msg":"女人有遺書 但係唔敢死 得個男既信佢一齊死 自己死左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31f4978b05ab709af48d8e6257b5e5f476f50ff","tid":948642,"uid":848